<p><a href="http://www.zerohedge.com/news/2012-11-04/bitcoin-seen-through-eyes-central-banker#comment-2951115" rel="nofollow">http://www.zerohedge.com/news/2012-11-04/bitcoin-seen-through-eyes-central-banker#comment-2951115</a></p>

