<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-2950151">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Mon, 11/05/2012 - 19:11 | <a href="/news/2012-11-04/bitcoin-seen-through-eyes-central-banker#comment-2950151" class="active">2950151</a></span>
