<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-2946787">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Sun, 11/04/2012 - 17:29 | <a href="/news/2012-11-04/bitcoin-seen-through-eyes-central-banker#comment-2946787" class="active">2946787</a></span>
